title: exile (feat. Bon Iver)
description:
Taylor Swift and William Bowery wrote this song together, but it took a little bit for people to find out who William Bowery actually is.. Why the secrecy surrounding this song? Taylor had a very good reason!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? There's lots of ways to reach us!
